Execute a runnable on the main thread

```
param runnable

a Java object implementing java.lang.Runnable.

param synchronous

True if we should wait for the runnable to finish.
```

Hint: to make a runnable using JavaScript:

```
return new java.lang.Runnable() {
  run: function() {
    <do something here>
  }
};
```

Execute a callable on the main thread, returning its value

```
param jcallable

a Java object implementing java.util.concurrent.Callable

returns

the result of evaluating the callable's "call" method in the
main thread.
```

Hint: to make a callable using JavaScript:

```
var my_import_scope = new JavaImporter(java.util.concurrent.Callable);
with (my_import_scope) {
    return new Callable() {
        call: function {
            <do something that produces result>
            return result;
        }
    };
```
